The Interagency Commission on Educational and Job Training Coordination is hereby created. Its membership shall be composed of the following individuals, serving in an ex officio capacity:
The chairman of the Council on Postsecondary Education;
The president of the Council on Postsecondary Education;
The chairman of the Kentucky Board of Education;
The commissioner of the Department of Education;
The commissioner of the Department of Workforce Investment;
The chairman of the Board for the Kentucky Higher Education Assistance Authority; and
The president of the Kentucky Community and Technical College System.
